menu.xml can be customized and will not be over-written with updates
if you rename it menu-custom.xml

You can also customize your toolbar.conf and rename it toolbar-custom.conf
it will not be over-written
Change 'order = ?' in descending order. 15 buttons are shown.
The highest numbered will be at the left.
Delete the file to restore to defaults.

Customize your default values for any sub-routine by changing the values
in the treeview to the one that fits best your needs then
select Edit->Save values as defaults
Each time you add the same sub-routine, those values will be used
To restore all defaults, delete 'custom_defaults.conf' file or
edit the file and remove the section you want restored.
This file is never over-written